limited access
the backup floor is not meant as a backup day-to-day work environment
to keep the equipment functioning and secure
we plan to limit access except for test times and if we need to invoke the plan because of a work stoppage
escalation procedures
the plan will be as follows
i
during regular business hours a
announcement
you will be notified via the pa system if you need to move to the backup location
or
b
no announcement
if an obvious problem like a fire or power shutdown occurs
for example
