anne
i have reviewed the p&s agreement for triple lutz
from my perspective
it generally looks fine
i have a few comments
and invite pat mackin to add any he may have
in particular based on his review of section 0.0
in section 0.0
c
iv
there is a reference to any contract obligations
i believe this would include employment contracts
which do not appear to be identified specifically on any schedule unless the annual amount exceeds $0k
we may want to clarify that the disclosures are consistent with the provisions of section 0.0
iii
section 0.0 provides that we will not enter into any employee benefits not required by law
however
given that closing is pushed out so far in the future
we may want the flexibility to provide incentive bonuses for key personnel to stay with the company through closing
this may be done with the buyer's consent
but we may be tying our hands
section 0.0
e
contains a similar restriction on making payments to officers/directors
in addition
section 0.0 states that we won't enter into or amend any employment contracts
we do not renew employment contracts at a single time
and the contracts of key personnel may expire
do we want to tie our hands and be prohibited from amending/extending the agreements
section 0.0
l
also prohibits the modification/amendment of contracts with employees
in section 0.0
the wording
other than environmental laws
suggests that we are not in compliance with environmental laws
rephrasing that sentence to refer to the provision of the agreement may be preferable
in section 0.0
d
we promise that we haven't provided any gift of any kind to customers
i don't think we can say that
given that we regularly host client development outings
e.g
rodeo bbq tickets
golf tourneys
etc
and provide enron goodies to people all the time
perhaps a limitation on de minimus gifts would be more accurate
also
a reference to our code of ethics may work here
in section 0.0
a
iii
does the $0k threshhold include only cash value
or does it include equity grants that vest over time
a reference to
cash
payments would clarify
given that people here are compensated by stock options/restricted stock that vest over time
in section 0.0
d
i am not sure whether this transaction accelerates vesting
